## 6. Average Resolution Time by Priority

### Purpose

Compare average resolution time across case priority levels.

### Query

```sql
SELECT
    case_priority,
    ROUND(AVG(actual_resolution_days), 2) AS avg_resolution_days
FROM support_cases
WHERE actual_resolution_days IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY case_priority
ORDER BY case_priority;
```

### Result

| case_priority | avg_resolution_days |
|---|---:|
| P1 | 4.65 |
| P2 | 7.79 |
| P3 | 10.54 |
| P4 | 13.12 |

