## 9. Most Common Root Cause Categories

### Purpose

Identify the most frequent root cause categories across support cases.

### Query

```sql
SELECT
    root_cause_category,
    COUNT(*) AS total_cases
FROM support_cases
WHERE root_cause_category IS NOT NULL
  AND root_cause_category <> ''
GROUP BY root_cause_category
ORDER BY total_cases DESC;
```

### Result

| root_cause_category | total_cases |
|---|---:|
| Configuration Issue | 119 |
| Connectivity Issue | 84 |
| User Error | 78 |
| Product Defect | 58 |
| Performance Issue | 57 |
| Database Issue | 50 |
| Environment Issue | 31 |
| Documentation Gap | 23 |

