# Initial Business Observations

- The dataset contains **500 support cases**.
- Most cases are already closed: **449 closed cases**, representing **89.8%** of the dataset.
- **P3 cases** represent the largest priority group with **213 cases**.
- **Integration Server** has the highest case volume with **170 cases**, representing **34%** of all cases.
- Overall SLA compliance for closed cases is **43.88%**, meaning more than half of closed cases breached the SLA target.
- SLA compliance is lowest for **P1 cases**, with only **13.04%** resolved within SLA.
- **API Gateway** has the highest SLA breach rate by component at **61.70%**, followed closely by **Integration Server** at **60.00%**.
- The most common root cause category is **Configuration Issue**, with **119 cases**.

